_:N96e915a458294a6ca15a28e3305d5050 <http://schema.org/description> "The Office for the Pay Review Bodies provides an independent secretariat to 8 Pay Review Bodies which make recommendations impacting 2.5 million workers – around 45% of public sector staff – and a pay bill of £100 billion. " .
